le differences between void and wall AGN might be\nexplained by a longer, less disturbed duty cycle of these systems in voids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2007 20:01:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
